---
import MainLayout from "../../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
---

<MainLayout title="Turning Raw Data into Revenue | Case Study">
  <div class="project-detail-bg">
    <div class="project-detail-card">
      <a href="/case-studies" class="back-button">&larr; Back to Case Studies</a>
      <div class="project-detail-content">
        <h1>How We Turned Raw Clinical Data into Revenue-Ready Assets</h1>
        <p class="summary">
          A pharmaceutical analytics company had billions of raw claims records
          sitting in their data warehouse — but couldn't monetize them due to
          compliance concerns and messy data quality. We built the transformation
          layer that made it all possible.
        </p>

        <h2>The Challenge</h2>
        <p>
          The client needed to process upstream claims transactions into clean,
          de-identified datasets that met strict NCPDP standards and HIPAA
          privacy requirements — all while maintaining full audit trails and
          supporting both daily automated runs and ad-hoc historical backfills.
        </p>

        <h2>What We Built</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>
            Collaborated with data science and business teams to identify and
            validate the right upstream datasets for claims processing.
          </li>
          <li>
            Built business-critical analytic views integrated into the
            downstream transformation pipeline for nightly and on-demand
            processing.
          </li>
          <li>
            Created a parameterized Snowflake stored procedure that
            de-identified and transformed claims according to NCPDP standards.
          </li>
          <li>
            Automated daily processing with Snowflake tasks, loading qualifying
            records into a master table for analytics and delivery.
          </li>
          <li>
            Supported manual historical runs for multi-year data backfills.
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Quality & Compliance</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>
            Comprehensive metadata logging for full transparency, audit
            support, and troubleshooting.
          </li>
          <li>
            Documented, compliant de-identification rules with clear separation
            of creation, validation, and execution responsibilities.
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Results</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>
            Secure, NCPDP-compliant de-identified datasets ready for
            tokenization and client delivery.
          </li>
          <li>
            Automated and on-demand delivery with full compliance and
            documented data lineage.
          </li>
          <li>
            This stage became the foundation for a platform now generating
            <strong>$7M+ in annual revenue</strong>.
          </li>
        </ul>

        <div class="tech-stack-detail">
          <strong>Tech:</strong>
          <span>Snowflake</span>
          <span>SQL</span>
          <span>AWS</span>
          <span>ETL Orchestration</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <style>
    .project-detail-bg {
      min-height: 100vh;
      width: 100vw;
      background:
        linear-gradient(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.78), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7)),
        url("/images/case_studies_tech.png") no-repeat center center;
      background-size: cover;
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      justify-content: center;
      padding-top: 72px;
    }
    .project-detail-card {
      max-width: 830px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      width: 100%;
      background: rgba(25, 30, 55, 0.68);
      border-radius: 22px;
      padding: 48px 40px 52px 40px;
      box-shadow: 0 16px 44px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.13);
      backdrop-filter: blur(14px) saturate(130%);
    }
    .back-button {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: #2997ff;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
      transition: color 0.2s;
    }
    .back-button:hover {
      color: #147bcd;
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
    .project-detail-content {
      color: #f5f5f7;
    }
    h1 {
      color: #2997ff;
      font-size: 2.1rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 0.9rem;
    }
    .summary {
      font-size: 1.13rem;
      color: #f5f5f7;
      margin-bottom: 1.4rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    p {
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      color: #d2d2d7;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    h2 {
      font-size: 1.18rem;
      color: #79bbff;
      margin-top: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.7rem;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    ul {
      margin: 0;
      margin-bottom: 1.1rem;
      padding-left: 1.2em;
    }
    ul li {
      font-size: 1.07rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.22em;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .tech-stack-detail {
      margin-top: 2.2rem;
      padding: 0.7rem 0.9rem;
      background: rgba(41, 151, 255, 0.09);
      border-radius: 13px;
      font-size: 1.02rem;
      color: #2997ff;
      font-weight: 500;
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 14px;
      align-items: center;
    }
    .tech-stack-detail strong {
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-right: 10px;
      color: #147bcd;
    }
    @media (max-width: 800px) {
      .project-detail-card {
        padding: 20px 8px 22px 8px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</MainLayout>
